# Expense Capital Computer Software Amount

## identifier
de15148

## type
float

## definition
The value of all capital expenditure for computer software.

## guidance
It includes: capitalised computer software license fees; installation costs; purchase or development of large databases; computer software developed in-house; and capitalised payments to contractors and consultants for software development. It excludes: computer software expensed; and software maintenance.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.CapitalComputerSoftware.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr1.02.35
- period=duration
